<h1>Race Weekends</h1>

<% @weekends.each do |weekend| %>
  <%= link_to "#{weekend.gp_title} - #{weekend.timespan}", weekend_path(weekend) %>
  <br><br>
<% end %>
<br><br>
<% if Rails.env.production? && !cookies[:authed] %>
  <%= link_to "Authenticate", auth_path %>
<% end %>
<% if cookies[:authed] %>
  <%= link_to "New Weekend", new_weekend_path %>
<% end %>
<br><br>
Admin functions use a cookie but I store zero information besides that you've logged in here. Check the source code if you want to be sure.
